{"tid":2364881,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國女YouTuber月花近3萬伙食費 勁過港大學生人工近倍","createTime":"2021-01-13T10:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T10:38:41.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f8490aabbd80186855e6555db3da2b8e320abc7c","tid":2364881,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FzmloooikW-xPtglbWshm45fJTA=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZLYKJHGPWJH53LLCXJ3JMCNK44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFzmloooikW-xPtglbWshm45fJTA%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZLYKJHGPWJH53LLCXJ3JMCNK44.jpg&h=480f0868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nYouTuber「挑食的小太陽」月花近3萬港元做伙食費。<br />\n<br />\n韓國吃播節目相當流行，當中直播主與觀眾互動的同時吃掉大量食物，滿足網絡觀眾的需求，他們當中愛在YouTube上做直播，同時與廣告商合作以賺取金錢。近日一名在YouTube上擁有158萬訂閱的吃播YouTuber「挑食的小太陽」（音譯），她就在頻道內進行「Q &amp; A」環節，當中更大爆自己一個月的伙食費用高達400萬韓圜（約28,350港元），比一個香港本年度大專畢業生首份工作的平均月薪多出近1倍。<br />\n<br />\n與愛犬在一起最幸福<br />\n「挑食的小太陽」在其頻道內邊吃東西邊與fans分享自己日常的瑣碎故事，有fans就好奇她1個月的伙食費，她就說：「最近用了很多，每天花20至30萬韓圜，1個月大概能花400萬韓圜。」對於結婚計劃，她就表示：「沒有結婚計劃。如果有伴侶先會計劃。」而「挑食的小太陽」因為亦有參與飲食節目的演出，所以為人認識，問到想更加有名氣還是現在已經很好時，她就直言：「比現在稍微不太出名但又能賺錢的話更好。」她亦坦言自己最幸福的瞬間就是與愛犬一起在陽光下躺着的時候。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/K3p5meFmG_qSllfc3btAMGNhnoc=/802x452/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/X2QTX3GLDZDG5ILTNEWYT3D4CE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FK3p5meFmG_qSllfc3btAMGNhnoc%3D%2F802x452%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FX2QTX3GLDZDG5ILTNEWYT3D4CE.jpg&h=ac0f2514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/10WTb-0DOfif4iFIbttnprl80mQ=/802x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FIPJDOKSEFHH5FJ2P654QHVPWA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F10WTb-0DOfif4iFIbttnprl80mQ%3D%2F802x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFIPJDOKSEFHH5FJ2P654QHVPWA.JPG&h=4377a9ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210112/JDCDGCAA3JEOJLWJ55J6NNVMLU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210112%2FJDCDGCAA3JEOJLWJ55J6NNVMLU%2F&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEYR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=ff766b62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210112%2FJDCDGCAA3JEOJLWJ55J6NNVMLU%2F&h=79f1abfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210112/JDCDGCAA3JEOJLWJ55J6NNVMLU/</a>"},{"pid":"eeab96b72222aa9c127bef398ce8322a5063801d","tid":2364881,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:27:29.000Z","msg":"發達大計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a61678f8cffe154b2fd961f26333a9fcce679380","tid":2364881,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeab96b72222aa9c127bef398ce8322a5063801d","tid":2364881,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:27:29.000Z","msg":"發達大計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:29:28.000Z","msg":"easy easy <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e3e49297fc09cd7530927ae4c7939a9e917645","tid":2364881,"uid":39383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:36:30.000Z","msg":"但假食, show 黎啫"},{"pid":"2b87ff4348ca056e90150057bf5b0929e77ee1bf","tid":2364881,"uid":42064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:38:41.000Z","msg":"係咪on9，拎百幾萬訂閱同fresh grad比。<br />\n大J唔夠百萬訂閱，都認自己最高曾經試過youtube ad有十萬蚊一個月。<br />\n<br />\n你當個韓國人口五千幾萬，做youtube易撈咁多，月入十萬應該大把人做到"}]}